    "name": "A Tale to Believe In",
    "prerequisite": "*Field Propagandist Dedication*",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You recite a tale of prowess that rewrites the combat unfolding around you. You can attempt a counteract check against a mental effect that's currently affecting an ally within 30 feet, using Deception for the counteract check and half your level as the counteract rank.",
